    "There is one qualification: initial unsupervised screening steps can be done before samples are left out.",
    "For example, we could select the 1000 predictors with highest variance across all 50 samples, before starting cross-validation.",
    "Since this filtering does not involve the class labels, it does not give the predictors an unfair advantage.",
    "The opposite opinion-that exploiting unlabeled test set features is unfair-may align more closely with best practices.",
